Hey! Kiŋ kaak gina gamin ŋuur-aŋku, kar iŋ taar-an oki, ki pakira a ki gediraaɗo pake min ɗo seriin ta Buŋdi walla?
Wal kiŋ kaak tal aminduwte-ak, ki aan̰ilaaɗo maman Buŋ giniy selliŋkaw? Ŋa gin subirraw dakina ho ŋa ica subirraw oki. Ki ibanno kadar Buŋ kat giniy selliŋkaw-aka a kii ibinin̰ nigin̰jiŋ.
Kar kiŋ gay, ka ɗeŋginko bombo ho ki pooc ibinin̰ nigin̰ji-ak, ansi-ak, ki nigaag adiy ka meen̰ji iŋ dapin̰ko ta Buŋdi ɗo ƴiriy taat ŋaa gaarin dapin̰koy ho seriin ta Buŋdi taat iŋ botilti yaa ase.
Ka seener gay, Buŋ yaaji kappiye ɗo ay gemo ɗo riy taat ŋa gintu.
