Ampaa ko, diŋka-aŋ, ŋu pooc karmiyin̰ Buŋ a ŋaaco tale aminduwco ar kaak ŋa taliŋko.
Asaan Buŋ, ŋaar ɗuuniig gee okin̰co ɗo ɓerrin kuuk karmiygigɗo. Ansii ko, ŋaa tale aminduwco ɗo gee okin̰co.
Gee iban tam kadar Buŋ, ŋaar gin ilim dakina ho ŋa iban gamin dakina! Ginno gem kaak yaa ibinin pikirrey wala ŋaa ibinin̰ji! Ho waan gediraaɗo ibinin̰ botilay kuuk ŋa rakiyo.
Ka seener gay, ŋu siir ɗo Kitamner aman: " Waa ibingit pikirre ta Buŋdi? Ho waa kaak nec taaƴin̰ji? "
" Waa di berji maanna a ŋaaji kappiyinti? "
