Nun gay kaawaako iŋ barkin taat Buŋ beriidu a naako kaawe ɗo ay gemo. Dakoŋ pakirenno ɗo goyiŋko kadar ku pakira ɗo goyiŋko kaak pakgigɗo. Kar gay, zeeɗoŋ kuu pakirenno ɗo goyiŋko kaak ku pakgigɗo. Ampa-ak, pakiroŋ ɗo goyiŋko kaak Buŋ berji imaan.
Ka seener, ay gem di gin gamin dakina ɗo zi ka gemor, kar gamin okin̰co-aŋ gay ginno riyoy.
Ansii ko, ginte okinte, ginte okinte ar zi ka gem rakki di iŋ n̰ume kaak gi n̰umtu iŋ Iisa Masi. Ampaa ko, ay gem di, ginte okinte n̰um ar zi ka gem rakki.
Ginte gin bere kaak riyco bere ɗo geemir ho bere kaak Buŋ beriite ar taat Buŋ beriite. Gem kaak gin bere kaak a ŋaa kaawe kaawin kuuk asa min ɗo Buŋdi, illa ŋaa kaawe ar nabiin̰ce. Gem-ak yaa kaawe ar kaak Buŋ beriiji ɗo gemor, illa ŋaa gaarin̰ji ar kaak ŋa diytu ɗo Iisa Masi ɗo bi ka imaanji.
Ya ŋu berji bere ka gaare ka Buŋdi a ŋaa gine riy ɗo Buŋdi, illa ŋaa gine riy taar-ata. Ya ŋu berji bere ka ɓilde geemir gay, illa ŋaa ɓilde geemir di.
Ya gem kaak iska gee ɗo imaan-ak, ŋa iskaagu. Ya ŋa bera bere ɗo een̰ji gay, ŋaa bere iŋ galal. Ya ŋa ogira gee, ŋaa gooƴe iŋ galal. Ya ŋa tala amindaw ta een̰ji, ŋaa tale iŋ galal.
Ele kaak ku elgiy ziŋkiko-ak, illa kuu ginguwe ka seener. Yampa, rasoŋ gamin kuuk samaanno, kar kat, kuu obe ŋuur kuuk samaane.
Elguwoŋ ziŋkiko ar siŋta kuuk tacco rakki. Ho ay gem di yaa bere horoomin ɗo eeŋko a ŋuu pakin̰ ziŋkiko.
Dakoŋ ginenno zegilay. Kar gay, ginon̰co riy iŋ gelbin rakki ho indiguwoŋ Rabbin Iisa Masi iŋ gelbin rakki.
Aditko yaa gine portiko ɗo maan kaak ku eriy iŋ imaanko. Ya ku taaɓiyaako, icoŋ subirraw ho dakoŋ peyenno ɗo salaanko.
Gaayguwoŋ gee ku Buŋdi kuuk goy ɗo pokirraw-ata ho goyoŋ goye ka martir.
Indon̰co barkin ta Buŋdi ɗo ŋuur kuuk taaɓiyaako. Barkiyon̰co ho dakoŋ surenno.
Aaciyoŋ iŋ ŋuur kuuk aaciyaw. Aloŋ iŋ ŋuur kuuk alaw.
Kar gay, goyoŋ goye ka aapiyer benanniko. Dakoŋ jaalenno ziŋkiko, dakoŋ talenno ziŋkiko ho dakoŋ talintiɗo ziŋkiko.
Ya waan ginko maan kaak samaanno, dakoŋ yeepintiɗo. Taloŋ ja samaane kuu gine taat gee okin̰co pakira a ŋa samaane.
Zeeɗoŋ a kuu goye iŋ gee okin̰co iŋ aapiye ar taat Buŋ rakiyo, ya kuu gedire kuu gine aapiye iŋ ŋuura.
Gem kol roynay, dakoŋ yeepin̰coɗo ziŋkiko a kuŋ sa yaaco yeepin̰ maan kaak kuuniye. Kar gay, rasoŋ maan kaak Buŋ rakiyo a kuu yeepin̰co ɗo maan kaak kuuniye. Asaan ɗo Kitamner, Rabbin Buŋ kaaw aman: " Ŋa nun kat yaa yeepin̰ ziŋkar ɗo maan kaak kuuniye. "
Ansii ko, ŋu siir ɗo Kitamner aman: " Ya adinen̰ adiy mey diyaaga, berji tee ho ya ŋa ibin diyaaga, berji see. Ya ki gina pa-ak, kii sokumin̰ ako. "
Dakoŋ rasenno botol taat samaanno kuuji pile. Kar gay, jaalguwoŋ taat samaanno iŋ selliŋkaw.
Ɗo goyiŋko, karmiyoŋ gee okin̰co kuuk hokumiyaako. Asaan ginno izinne ya Buŋ balco bere izinne. Ho ŋuur kuuk gin izinne-ak, Buŋ kat diyig ɗo werco.
Ŋaar-ak, gem kaak poocaat izinne ta agindaw ku Buŋdi, ŋa poocaat izinne taat Buŋ kaawtu. Kar gem kaak poocaat izinne ta meen̰ji gay, seriin Buŋ yaa obin̰ji.
Ka seener, gee kuuk gina taat samaane, ŋuur ginaaɗo kolaw ɗo aginduwco, illa ŋuur kuuk gina taat samaanno. Ki rakaaɗo gine kolaw ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi walla? Di ŋaar-ak, ginit taat samaane ho ŋaan̰ ozilin̰ciŋ.
Asaan ka seener, *gaanuun ka tatko, ŋaar gay riyor ka Buŋdi kaak ginaat a kii gine maan kaak gala. Kar ya ki gina maan kaak samaanno gay, ginno kolaw. Ka seener gay, ŋaar ucaaɗo *seepinpan ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Kar gay, ka seener, ŋa gay riyor ka Buŋdi kaak ginaat iŋ gudurre ta meen̰ji a ŋaa taaɓiyin̰ ŋuur kuuk gina taat samaanno ho ŋaaji ɗukume seriin ɗo kaƴco.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, kuu karmiyin̰ agindaw kuuk hokumiyaako-aku. Ɗo saan taar-an, dakoŋ karmiyenno ɗo saan ta kolaw di, kar gay, illa pikirriko oki yaa ose.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ku kappiygiy miiri, asaan aginduwco ku gay riyor ku Buŋdi, asaan ŋu giniit riyco a ŋuu kappiyin riyoy-ata.
Ɗoƴoŋ ɗo gee okin̰co maan kaak yaaco bere miiri ɗo ŋuur okin̰co. Beron̰jiŋ miiri ɗo ŋuur kuuk hariyaako, ho beron̰jiig miiri ɗo ŋuur kuuk hariyaako. Beron̰jiig horoomine ɗo ŋuur kuuk karmiyaaga ho beron̰co horoomine ɗo ŋuur kuuk karmiyaaga.
Dakoŋ obenno gamin okin̰co kuuk yaa nece ɗo eeŋko, illa kuu elguwe ziŋkiko. Ka seener, gem kaak el een̰ji, ŋaar necit gaanuun okin̰ji.
Ɗo gaanuun-aŋ, kaawin kuuk ŋu siirtu ɗo Kitamner aman: " Kuŋ miday, dakoŋ kokinenno daaɗ kara ho kuŋ daaɗ oki, dakoŋ kokinenno miday kara, okiŋko, dakoŋ deenno gee, dakoŋ kokinenno gamna ku gemor, dakoŋ kokinenno gamna ku gemor. " Kaawin okin̰co kuuk gaanuun-aŋ, okin̰co, ŋuur n̰um ɗo kaaw rakki di: " Kii elin̰ giji ar zin̰ ka meen̰jiŋ. "
Gem kaak el giji, ŋaar ginaagɗo maan kaak samaanno ɗo giji. Ampa-ak, ya gem kaak el een̰ji, ŋaar-ak necit kaaw ta gaanuun okintiti.
Diyoŋ ɗo kaƴko, diŋ ku iban maman diŋ ku goyiy ɗo duniiner. Diŋ wiktinti nec ko taat kuu weƴe min ɗo weƴiŋko. Ka seener, diŋka-aŋ, jile kaak Buŋ yaate jilinte pakgig wiktin taat gi aamintu ɗo Iisa Masi.
Jemma-an, taar gaay ko mate ho ƴiriyo sa gaay ko mate. Ŋaar-ak, rasoŋ gamin kuuk jookumo kuuk jookumo ho isinteŋ gamin ku taasin̰kar kuuk goy ɗo portikaw.
Goyinte ar gee kuuk goy ɗo botildi ar ŋu goyiy iŋ ƴiriyo. Gininte ɗo gamin kuuk arro, iŋ sakriyaw, iŋ ɓaaƴe kaak mun̰jam, iŋ ɓaaƴe kaak mun̰jam, iŋ giɗaw, ho iŋ hasuudinaw oki.
Iŋ taar-at ko, siyoŋ ziŋkiko kadar Rabbin Iisa Masi sa, ŋaar ar kaak kuuniy ziŋkiko. Dakoŋ rawtenno pey galal ta ziŋkiko ho dakoŋ aaɗin̰coɗo taat samaanno.
Ya waan gin imaanji sooɗa, obon̰ji samaane ho dakoŋ osenno ziŋkiko ɗo maan kaak ŋa pakiriyɗo ɗo imaanji.
Toŋgo-aŋ, gem rakki gin imaan a ŋaa gedire tee ay maanna, kar ŋaar kaak imaanji sooɗ gay, ŋa aawa tee kaak aawa maala.
Ŋaar kaak tiya gamin okin̰co-aŋ, illa ŋaa aan̰in̰jiɗo ŋaar kaak tiyaagɗo gamin okin̰co-aŋka. Ŋaar kaak tiyaagɗo gamin okin̰co-aŋ sa, illa ŋaa diyenno kaaw ɗo gem kaak tiyaagɗo gamin okin̰co-aŋku, asaan Buŋ ooyit ko iŋ ŋaara.
Kiŋke waa kina a kii deen̰ gay riyor ka gem rakki? Ya ŋa zeeɗa wal ŋaa gale oki, riy-at ta tatkuwiy di yaaji aawe gala. Kar gay, illa tatkuwiy kat yaaji ɗake, asaan *Rabbin Buŋ gin gudurre taat ŋaa diyin̰ji ɗo werti.
Ɗo uŋji ka gemor, gem rakki pakira a ƴiriy rakki, ŋaar pakira a ƴiriy rakki, taar pakgig serek. Kar gem rakki gay pakira a ƴiriy rakki sa, okin̰co, illa ay gemo yaa ibine waraŋ ɗo gelbiney.
Ŋaar kaak pakira a ƴiriy rakki, ŋa pakira a ŋa samaane ɗo maan kaak *Rabbin Iisa Masi giniyo. Ho ŋaar kaak tiyaag tee okin̰ji-ak, ŋa pakira a ŋa samaane ɗo saan ta Rabbin Iisa Masi, asaan ŋa dela barkin ɗo Buŋdi ɗo bi kan̰ji. Kar ŋaar kaak tiyaagɗo tee okin̰ji-ak, ŋa pakira a ŋa samaane ɗo saan ta Rabbin Iisa Masi ho ŋa dela barkin ɗo Buŋdi oki.
Asaan minninni, ginno gem kaak goya ɗo kaay ka meen̰ji di ho ginno gem kaak mata ɗo kaay ka meen̰ji di.
Ya gi goya, gi goya ɗo uŋji ka Rabbin Buŋ, ho ya gi mate, gi mate ɗo uŋji ka Rabbin Buŋ. Ya gi goya wala gi mate, ginte ku Rabbin Buŋ.
*Masi kaak Buŋ doɓtu-ak, ŋaar mattu ho ŋa nooytu pey ɗo muuti a ŋaa gine *Rabbine ka gee kuuk goy mento ho iŋ kuuk mate oki.
Kiŋke-aŋ gay, maa di ki ɗukumiiji kaaw ɗo siŋjiŋ kaak aamin ɗo Iisa Masi? Wal kiŋke-aŋ gay, maa di ki talaag siŋjiŋ ar maan ka maala? Ginte okinte, gi ɓaa ɗo wer ka seriiner kaak Buŋ asiy ɗukume seriine.
asaan ŋu siir ɗo Kitamner aman: ‟ Rabbin Buŋ kaaw aman: ‟ Nun ka seener, iŋ siŋ kunto, ay gemo yaa derse uŋdu ɗo uŋdu, ho ay gemo yaa kaawe ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi a nu Buŋdi. " "
